     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "ChebyshevCoefficients[poly, n] returns a list {c0, c1, c2, ..., c n - 1} \
of n Chebyshev expansion coefficients of polynomial poly of degree d = n - 1 \
or less. ChebyshevCoefficients[poly, n -> parity] returns the n non-zero \
Chebyshev expansion coefficients {c0, c2, c4, ..., c 2 (n - 1)} or {c1, c3, \
c5, ..., c 2 n - 1} of even (parity = +1) or odd (parity = -1) polynomial \
poly of degree d = 2 (n - 1) or n = 2 n - 1, respectively, by evaluating poly \
only on the positive side of the domain, [0, 1].", "synonyms" -> {}, 
